                    "required": 0,
                    "conditional_logic": 0,
                    "wrapper": {
                        "width": "",
                        "class": "",
                        "id": ""
                    },
                    "default_value": "The joint venture between ADNOC Drilling, SLB and Patterson-UTI developed to deliver the well construction and completion program for Abu Dhabi spanning from the Ruwais Diyab Unconventional Gas Concession across Abu Dhabi’s Al Dhafra region to the Falaha and Huwaila oil fields.\r\n\r\nWell delivery cycles have compressed from approximately 40 days to as few as 13.5 days.\r\n\r\nThe Turnwell JV leverages leading innovations in AI, smart drilling design, completions engineering and production solutions alongside global experience and knowledge to reach best-in-class efficiency and well performance.\r\n\r\nDriven by world-class expertise, Turnwell transforms client challenges into optimized outcomes through seamless integrated services and comprehensive project management.",
